{"bill": {"#text": "\n\t", "form": {"current-chamber": {"#tail": "\n\t\t", "#text": "IN THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES"}, "#text": "\n\t\t", "congress": {"#tail": "\n\t\t", "#text": "113th CONGRESS"}, "#tail": "\n\t", "legis-num": {"#tail": "\n\t\t", "#text": "H. R. 2241"}, "official-title": {"#tail": "\n\t", "#text": "To amend the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 to provide a\n\t\t  credit for owning certain disaster resilient property."}, "session": {"#tail": "\n\t\t", "#text": "1st Session"}, "distribution-code": {"#tail": "\n\t\t", "@display": "yes", "#text": "I"}, "action": {"action-date": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t", "@date": "20130604", "#text": "June 4, 2013"}, "#tail": "\n\t\t", "action-desc": {"#tail": "\n\t\t", "#text": "\n        ", "committee-name": {"#tail": "\n      ", "@committee-id": "HWM00", "#text": "Committee on Ways and Means"}, "sponsor": {"#tail": " (for\n\t\t\t himself and ", "#text": "Mr. Diaz-Balart", "@name-id": "D000600"}, "cosponsor": {"#tail": ") introduced the\n\t\t\t following bill; which was referred to the ", "#text": "Mr. Harris", "@name-id": "H001052"}}, "#text": "\n\t\t\t"}, "legis-type": {"#tail": "\n\t\t", "#text": "A BILL"}}, "@bill-stage": "Introduced-in-House", "@bill-type": "olc", "@dms-id": "HD9FC00159C694A44B446216EEE176FE8", "@public-private": "public", "legis-body": {"#tail": "\n", "@style": "OLC", "section": [{"@section-type": "section-one", "#tail": "\n    ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t", "quote": {"short-title": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "Disaster Savings and Resilient\n\t\t\t Construction Act of 2013"}, "#tail": ".", "#text": "\n          "}, "#text": "This Act may be cited as the\n\t\t\t ", "@display-inline": "no-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n      ", "#text": "1."}, "header": {"#tail": "\n      ", "#text": "Short title"}, "#text": "\n      ", "@id": "H7DAE82C1E2B64EBEADF4A1D3B86F6D99"}, {"#tail": "\n  ", "enum": {"#tail": "\n      ", "#text": "2."}, "header": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t", "#text": "Disaster\n\t\t\t resilient property tax credit"}, "subsection": [{"#tail": "\n      ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": [{"#tail": " is amended by inserting after ", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "Subpart D of part IV of subchapter A of chapter 1 of the\n\t\t\t Internal Revenue Code of 1986", "@value": "Internal Revenue Code of 1986/ch:1/sch:A/pt:IV/spt:D"}, {"#tail": " the\n\t\t\t following new section:", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "section 30D", "@value": "Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:30D"}], "#text": "\n          "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "(a)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "In\n\t\t\t general"}, "quoted-block": {"@style": "OLC", "after-quoted-block": {"#tail": "\n        ", "#text": "."}, "#tail": "\n\t\t\t", "section": {"#tail": "\n          ", "enum": {"#tail": "\n            ", "#text": "30E."}, "header": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "Disaster\n\t\t\t\tresilient property"}, "subsection": [{"#tail": "\n            ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "There shall be allowed\n\t\t\t\tas a credit against the tax imposed by this chapter for the taxable year an\n\t\t\t\tamount equal to the applicable amount for each qualified building placed in\n\t\t\t\tservice during the taxable year.", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "(a)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "General\n\t\t\t\trule"}, "#text": "\n              ", "@id": "HEC603B2A79AD412D8E5086DC61A7C799"}, {"#tail": "\n            ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": {"#tail": "\u2014", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "subsection (a)", "@value": "Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:30E/ss:a", "@proposed": "true"}, "#text": "For purposes of "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "(b)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "Applicable\n\t\t\t\tamount"}, "paragraph": [{"#tail": "\n              ", "@id": "H7274FEEB705343A18F79BE6A8219765B", "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "(1)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "Commercial\n\t\t\t\tproperty"}, "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "In the case of a qualified commercial property, the\n\t\t\t\tapplicable amount is the lesser of\u2014"}, "#text": "\n                ", "subparagraph": [{"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "1 percent of the\n\t\t\t\tcost of the building, or"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(A)"}, "@id": "H193EF2F3CD5D42CEAE3A61D82E2F13D2", "#text": "\n                  "}, {"#tail": "\n              ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "$25,000 per\n\t\t\t\tbuilding."}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(B)"}, "@id": "H582BD223935043F89C6B3D1E402B144B", "#text": "\n                  "}]}, {"#tail": "\n            ", "@id": "H0E111B5A9E994AC3A427164BC2334A6B", "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "(2)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "Residential\n\t\t\t\tproperty"}, "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "In the case of a qualified residential property, the\n\t\t\t\tapplicable amount is the lesser of\u2014"}, "#text": "\n                ", "subparagraph": [{"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "1 percent of the\n\t\t\t\tcost of the property (or construction cost for rehabilitation of the property),\n\t\t\t\tor"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(A)"}, "@id": "HD1F422BA9195420792BB8E776E55D966", "#text": "\n                  "}, {"#tail": "\n              ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "$3,000 per\n\t\t\t\tproperty."}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(B)"}, "@id": "HF1A358A5B8E249CEBEB03645732D5E84", "#text": "\n                  "}]}], "#text": "\n              ", "@id": "H683D72C25A2B4FB091A4F8D953BDD17B"}, {"#tail": "\n            ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": {"#tail": "\u2014", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "subsection (a)", "@value": "Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:30E/ss:a", "@proposed": "true"}, "#text": "For purposes of "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "(c)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "Qualified\n\t\t\t\tbuilding"}, "paragraph": [{"#tail": "\n              ", "@id": "HF528C1DE219B4473B9F446F53AB2880C", "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "(1)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "In\n\t\t\t\tgeneral"}, "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "term": {"#tail": " means a\n\t\t\t\tbuilding\u2014", "#text": "qualified building"}, "#text": "The term "}, "#text": "\n                ", "subparagraph": [{"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "owned by the\n\t\t\t\ttaxpayer in a disaster area determined as a result of a federally declared\n\t\t\t\tmajor disaster,"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(A)"}, "@id": "HA546EC9167B74D32AF1FD33F912ED72F", "#text": "\n                  "}, {"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "the construction\n\t\t\t\tof which began after the date of such disaster in that area,"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(B)"}, "@id": "H703D4E2E8B61418393EDF83A26D2DC9B", "#text": "\n                  "}, {"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "which\u2014"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(C)"}, "clause": [{"#tail": "\n                  ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "is\n\t\t\t\tqualified commercial property placed in service for commercial purposes,\n\t\t\t\tor"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(i)"}, "@id": "H2FF2DB9459C549DB9C2EE66495ED77CC", "#text": "\n                    "}, {"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "is qualified\n\t\t\t\tresidential property is placed in service for residential purposes, and"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(ii)"}, "@id": "H4365D55A770743CE8E942AF0F289DEC5", "#text": "\n                    "}], "#text": "\n                  ", "@id": "HC767977921554DBEB7B34D0599985509"}, {"#tail": "\n              ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "for which a\n\t\t\t\tcertificate of occupancy is issued before the end of the 3-year period\n\t\t\t\tbeginning on the date of such disaster declaration in that area."}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(D)"}, "@id": "H64218D4C3EDA4E5C90478E0F53884C71", "#text": "\n                  "}]}, {"#tail": "\n              ", "@id": "HEF5FFCC963784E8980B0C00912AF393C", "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "(2)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "Qualified\n\t\t\t\tcommercial property"}, "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "term": {"#tail": " means a building that is\u2014", "#text": "qualified commercial\n\t\t\t\tproperty"}, "#text": "The term "}, "#text": "\n                ", "subparagraph": [{"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "located in the\n\t\t\t\tUnited States,"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(A)"}, "@id": "HB4C093E9E5D9446BB73679567DC62DDC", "#text": "\n                  "}, {"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "defined in the\n\t\t\t\tscope of the 2009 or later International Building Code published by the\n\t\t\t\tInternational Code Council, and"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(B)"}, "@id": "H4C4504C68DC74E98A2C6947E61BF88B1", "#text": "\n                  "}, {"#tail": "\n              ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "designed and\n\t\t\t\tconstructed to meet resilient construction requirements."}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(C)"}, "@id": "H1CB3A1D46FDD4D6EA2A5D0CF2FA863FD", "#text": "\n                  "}]}, {"#tail": "\n            ", "@id": "H70FF6CD3093948E499E9066338EA714A", "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "(3)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "Qualified\n\t\t\t\tresidential property"}, "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "term": {"#tail": " means a building that is\u2014", "#text": "qualified residential\n\t\t\t\tproperty"}, "#text": "The term "}, "#text": "\n                ", "subparagraph": [{"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "located in the\n\t\t\t\tUnited States,"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(A)"}, "@id": "H39A6C3EE4A6B4DBA9BF273E4B592DD33", "#text": "\n                  "}, {"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "defined in the\n\t\t\t\tscope of the 2009 or later International Residential Code published by the\n\t\t\t\tInternational Code Council, and"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(B)"}, "@id": "H1B9E010B64F54B0E9A2EE595F15953D8", "#text": "\n                  "}, {"#tail": "\n              ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "designed and\n\t\t\t\tconstructed to meet resilient construction requirements."}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(C)"}, "@id": "H810020F87CA14531B42C4FA73F7B4FCF", "#text": "\n                  "}]}], "#text": "\n              ", "@id": "H32867FD1520240F4912069F533333BD5"}, {"#tail": "\n            ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "For purposes of this section\u2014"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "(d)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "Resilient\n\t\t\t\tconstruction requirements"}, "paragraph": [{"#tail": "\n              ", "@id": "H4D92391021F74A16B12C9ED86483EFD7", "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "(1)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "In\n\t\t\t\tgeneral"}, "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "The resilient construction requirements with respect to a\n\t\t\t\tproperty are that the property is designed and constructed to\u2014"}, "#text": "\n                ", "subparagraph": [{"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "resist hazards\n\t\t\t\tbrought on by a major disaster and continues to provide its primary functions\n\t\t\t\tafter a major disaster,"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(A)"}, "@id": "HD4DB9F14238040768EFF2424E636EB01", "#text": "\n                  "}, {"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "reduce the\n\t\t\t\tmagnitude or duration of a disruptive event, and"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(B)"}, "@id": "HE5C49724C13D4E70ACDC044F0F587E98", "#text": "\n                  "}, {"#tail": "\n              ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "have the\n\t\t\t\tabsorptive capacity, adaptive capacity, recoverability to withstand a\n\t\t\t\tpotentially disruptive event."}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(C)"}, "@id": "H3A465A096EB844449BFE53BC89D37F38", "#text": "\n                  "}]}, {"#tail": "\n              ", "@id": "HF32F51188FC745198204BD2F274E41FA", "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "(2)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "Treated as\n\t\t\t\tmeeting resiliency requirements"}, "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": {"#tail": "\u2014", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "paragraph\n\t\t\t\t(1)", "@value": "Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:30E/ss:d/p:1", "@proposed": "true"}, "#text": "For purposes of "}, "#text": "\n                ", "subparagraph": [{"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": {"#tail": " if the property is a building\n\t\t\t\twhich\u2014", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "paragraph (1)", "@value": "Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:30E/ss:d/p:1", "@proposed": "true"}, "#text": "in the case of a\n\t\t\t\tqualified commercial property, the property shall be treated as meeting the\n\t\t\t\trequirements specified in "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(A)"}, "clause": [{"#tail": "\n                  ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "was designed to\n\t\t\t\tmeet the requirements of the 2009 or later International Building Code\n\t\t\t\tpublished by the International Code Council and received the Insurance\n\t\t\t\tInstitute for Business and Home Safety FORTIFIED for Safer Business\n\t\t\t\tdesignation, or"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(i)"}, "@id": "H69CD6D02D3954DAAA51F16BB86D6E518", "#text": "\n                    "}, {"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "was designed and\n\t\t\t\tbuilt in a jurisdiction that requires commercial buildings to meet the\n\t\t\t\trequirements of the 2009 or later International Building Code published by the\n\t\t\t\tInternational Code Council with amendments that are equivalent or more\n\t\t\t\trestrictive than the requirements described in FORTIFIED for Safer Business\n\t\t\t\tStandards published by the Insurance Institute for Business and Home Safety and\n\t\t\t\treceived a certificate of occupancy (or other documentation stating that it has\n\t\t\t\tmet the requirements of the building code) from the jurisdiction, and"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(ii)"}, "@id": "H953F7189F47D4E02925853469A835EFF", "#text": "\n                    "}], "#text": "\n                  ", "@id": "H27193CA44A044565889C77C17CF10EA1"}, {"#tail": "\n              ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": {"#tail": " if the property is a building which was\n\t\t\t\tdesigned to meet the requirements of the 2009 or later International\n\t\t\t\tResidential Code published by the International Code Council, and meets one of\n\t\t\t\tthe following requirements:", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "paragraph (1)", "@value": "Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:30E/ss:d/p:1", "@proposed": "true"}, "#text": "in the case of a\n\t\t\t\tqualified residential property, the property shall be treated as meeting the\n\t\t\t\trequirements specified in "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(B)"}, "clause": [{"#tail": "\n                  ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "The building\n\t\t\t\treceived the Insurance Institute for Business and Home Safety as FORTIFIED for\n\t\t\t\tSafer Living designation."}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(i)"}, "@id": "H517A0F8554D74147897CC24D118DF3DD", "#text": "\n                    "}, {"#tail": "\n                  ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "The building\n\t\t\t\treceived the Insurance Institute for Business and Home Safety as FORTIFIED for\n\t\t\t\tExisting Homes designation, silver level."}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(ii)"}, "@id": "H1485D9CB34344F22BCF4BB9BA60903A3", "#text": "\n                    "}, {"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "It was designed\n\t\t\t\tand built in a jurisdiction that requires residential buildings to meet the\n\t\t\t\trequirements of the 2009 or later International Building Code published by the\n\t\t\t\tInternational Code Council with amendments that are equivalent or more\n\t\t\t\trestrictive than the requirements described in FORTIFIED for Safer Living\n\t\t\t\tBuilders Guide published by the Insurance Institute for Business and Home\n\t\t\t\tSafety and received a certificate of occupancy (or other documentation stating\n\t\t\t\tthat it has met the requirements of the building code) fr